snippet.title: Mooshie's Kitchen 3 - Indie Horror Game - No Commentary
snippet.description:
Thanks For Watching!

Facebook https://www.facebook.com/Stella-Abbasi-100150965166877/
Twitter https://twitter.com/StellaAbbasi

Download https://omogonixlachlan.itch.io/mooshies-kitchen-3

Mooshie has returned once more in the finale of the Mooshie's Kitchen trilogy. This time, he's the President of the United States!

In Mooshie's Kitchen 3, you play as a secret agent whose mission is to infiltrate President Mooshie's bunker and kill Mooshie once and for all!

Indie Horror Game Playlist https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk0tZ0YT3FZEsIgd3Qdj19xGe9VcMMI1P

#mooshieskitchen #Indiegames
